Package: astropack
Type: Package
Title: Astrology Utility Toolkit for Zodiac, Moon Phases, and Retrogrades
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Makayla", "Harvey",
      email = "mharvey33332@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: This package contains a collection of astrology-based R utilities that provide zodiac sign lookup, 
    horoscope retrieval, moon phase advice, and Mercury retrograde detection. 
    This packase also includes data sources from Horscopes.com (for horoscopes),
    Susan Miller's mercury retrograde calendar (2016-2030), and zodiac trait definitions from common astrological references.
    This package is built for research, spiritual planning, and teaching purposes.
